Effects of Investment Plans on CWS Performance

Hydrosystems Research Group

June 21, 2017

Use the figures below to investigate the data. The plot and the table are linked, so actions on one will impact the data on the other. Some tips:

  • Selecting rows on the table will higlight them on the plot. You can select multiple rows at a time.
  • Click and drag a selection box around points on the plot to filter the table to show only those points.
  • Double click on the plot to reset.
  • Use the arrows to the right of the column names to sort the table.
  • Hover over a point on the plot to see its cost and the investment plans used.

Note: the data point at (0, 0) is a bug and does not actually exist in the data. Kindly disregard.
